2C%20and%20started%20mapping%20it%20all%20out.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20drawing%20on%20a%20big%20chart%20paper%2C%20writing%20the%20whole%20plan%20for%20execution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurav%20says.%20The%20idea%20was%20simple%3A%20gather%20people%2C%20bring%20instruments%2C%20and%20just%20let%20the%20rhythms%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20first%20attempt%20gave%20us%20a%20reality%20check%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20plan%20in%20place%2C%20BDC%E2%80%99s%20first%20drum%20circle%20kicked%20off%20at%20Cubbon%20Park.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20anything%20big%20%E2%80%94%20just%20Gaurav%E2%80%99s%20friends%2C%20a%20few%20people%20who%20noticed%20them%20playing%20at%20the%20park%20and%20joined%20in%2C%20and%20a%20small%20circle%20forming%20on%20the%20grass.%20They%20were%20simply%20testing%20the%20waters%2C%20hoping%20to%20create%20a%20space%20where%20anyone%20could%20walk%20in%2C%20pick%20up%20a%20drum%2C%20and%20feel%20part%20of%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20officials%20came%20over%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20stop.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20asked%20us%20to%20stop%20whatever%20we%20were%20doing%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20court%20and%20there%20was%20some%20examination%20going%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurav%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-13T181144.051_11zon-1749819081.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22people%20at%20BDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the